nd scale for customers who have simpler everyday banking needs rbwm offers a full range of banking products and services reflecting local requirementscommercial bankingas of december   cmb served approximately two million customers in  countries and territories its customers range from small enterprises focused primarily on their domestic markets through to corporates operating globally it supports its customers with tailored financial products and services services provided include working capital term loans payment services and international trade facilitation among other services as well as expertise in mergers and acquisitions and access to financial marketsglobal banking and marketsas of december   gbm served approximately  clients in more than  countries and territories it supports government corporate and institutional clients across the world its product specialists continue to deliver a range of transaction banking financing advisory capital markets and risk management servicesglobal private bankingthe companys gpb business serves highnetworth individuals and families including those with international banking needs through booking centers covering its markets its products and services include investment management which incorporates advisory discretionary and brokerage services private wealth solutions which consists of trusts and estate planning designed to manage wealth and preserve it for future generations and a range of private banking services ¬ª full overview of hsbcn company address hsbc holdings plc  canada squarelondon ¬† ¬† e hq p  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation douglas¬†flint  stuart¬†gulliver  iain¬†mackay  andy¬†maguire  marc¬†moses  ¬ª more officers  directors hsbc holdings plc news bank of england opens up payments systems to spur fintech jul   bank of england opens up payments systems to spur fintech jul   update battered carillion drafts in hsbc amid rights issue talk jul   rptupdate battered carillion t